pr_body:
Adds the capability to view images on the OSM map from the local device or other sources per drag and
drop to the editor. Clicking on an appropriate marker of the image opens the image for display.

A common example in the form of a User Story can be

1.  An OSM user takes photos of different restaurants, supermarkets, and other cafes from his/her phone on a given day

2. The user now wants to update the opening and closing hours of one of the restaurants with help of the photos he/she took some time ago

3. By dragging and dropping (or importing) those photos in the iD editor, the user wants to see all the photos on the OSM & fill out the business hours (opening and closing) side-by-side

A pictorial representation can be found [here](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1h07KhUi3fVwpsIOWqb7nw310n8ja7wq9/view)
